            style="color: wheat; font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; font-size: 2 em; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5em;">
            Mountain Adventures</h1>

    </div>


